ce-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/015756_92a066569ee1ca6364151183cac0e652.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F015756_92a066569ee1ca6364151183cac0e652.png&h=11c037cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一,付國豪既入境標籤上面寫住訪客 批准逗留至2019年08月13日,佢係大約凌晨12點出現機場,已經係違反左入境條例,係屬於過期居留<br />\n<br />\n第二,根據入境處網頁(<a href=\"https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/useful_information/visit-transit/endorsement-samples.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.immd.gov.hk%2Fhkt%2Fuseful_information%2Fvisit-transit%2Fendorsement-samples.html&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHUyq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=9b3e6e54\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/useful_information/visit-transit/endorsement-samples.html</a>)佢係屬於訪客入境標籤,入黎香港係唔可以接受有薪或者無薪既工作,如果佢係黎香港做採訪工作,有機會屬於黑工<br />\n<br />\n加上係身上面又搵唔到記者證,環球時報只不過係鳩up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa6dcad78d297c978c3957d31b259260beaaafee","tid":1468500,"uid":227929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:08:25.000Z","msg":"佢都唔係記者<br />\n佢係用訪客身份入港"},{"pid":"a95e4b1eb9cf136a44145a3e2dc7af3095eb542d","tid":1468500,"uid":227929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:09:09.000Z","msg":"(正視聽)付國豪係香港唔係合法記者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468160\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468160</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<em></em>"},{"pid":"67d0bd34f690556f26fe172974deed3cdf97ac5a","tid":1468500,"uid":272186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e053de615d4177734244711b9ebfe5866069357","tid":1468500,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fe741a16399a5a0218905b74113bbe4a62a01123","tid":1468500,"uid":30006,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"205a277e7ede56f9580cb056233ee3ba75a47e1c","tid":1468500,"uid":79117,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:58:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">Civil Arrest真係一個最好既理由點解要捉佢</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:01:34.000Z","msg":"基於乜野原因 ?<br />\n<br />\n捉鬼唔係一個原因，無構成一個即時的公眾安全威脅<br />\n<br />\n你話搵到藍衫覺得佢係黑社會，有機會傷到人<br />\n<br />\n所以進行公民拘捕<br />\n<br />\n雖然唔係好夠牙力，但起碼方向正確先<br />\n<br />\n我開呢個post ,就係想大家用一個啱的方法補救自己的錯<br />\n<br />\n而唔係再造更多的錯出黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:04:00.000Z","msg":"我個諗法係同你一樣，件衫真係做拘捕既最大證據。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:21:03.000Z","msg":"加埋「承認唔完美、可接受，但會改善」"},{"pid":"77b7376b06945692468e12b928ec38d414944df3","tid":1468500,"uid":272186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e85184620fbdbeeab11c41f080f1a8d2f409653b","tid":1468500,"uid":17381,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:07:43.000Z","msg":"根據網上流傳相片<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9JOKMVo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9JOKMVo.jpg&h=03b54870&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/015756_92a066569ee1ca6364151183cac0e652.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F015756_92a066569ee1ca6364151183cac0e652.png&h=11c037cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一,付國豪既入境標籤上面寫住訪客 批准逗留至2019年08月13日,佢係大約凌晨12點出現機場,已經係違反左入境條例,係屬於過期居留<br />\n<br />\n第二,根據入境處網頁(<a href=\"https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/useful_information/visit-transit/endorsement-samples.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.immd.gov.hk%2Fhkt%2Fuseful_information%2Fvisit-transit%2Fendorsement-samples.html&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHUyq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=9b3e6e54\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/useful_information/visit-transit/endorsement-samples.html</a>)佢係屬於訪客入境標籤,入黎香港係唔可以接受有薪或者無薪既工作,如果佢係黎香港做採訪工作,有機會屬於黑工<br />\n<br />\n加上係身上面又搵唔到記者證,環球時報只不過係鳩up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:22:37.000Z","msg":"厲害<img src=\"/assets/f